Parliament, Tuesday, 24 April 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Services will today receive a briefing from the Information Regulator on capacity regarding its Annual Performance Plan and Budget. The committee will also be briefed by the National Prosecuting Authority (NPA) on its Annual Performance Plan and Budget. Details are as follows: 
	Date: 24 April 2018
	Time: 12:00 pm
	Venue: Committee Room V454, Fourth Floor, Old Assembly Building ISSUED BY PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON JUSTICE AND CORRECTIONAL SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
	Tel: 021 403 8437
	Cell: 081 703 9542
